{"tid":2076256,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"賑災基金110萬助廣西水災災民","createTime":"2020-06-23T11:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T11:43:52.000Z","uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"25f528c545858fd5e380f53be28de8cc24b8016c","tid":2076256,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:22:34.000Z","msg":"賑災基金撥款助廣西水災災民<br />\n<br />\n2020年6月23日<br />\n<br />\n政府從賑災基金批出110萬元予兩間機構，以賑濟廣西壯族自治區水災災民。<br />\n <br />\n撥款中55萬元給予愛德基金會（香港），55萬元給予樂施會，用於提供食米、食油和即食麵，約12,000名災民受惠。<br />\n <br />\n兩救援機構進行賑災的地點並不相同，沒有資源重疊。機構完成賑災計劃後須向賑災基金諮詢委員會呈交評估報告和經審核帳目，以確保撥款用於指定用途。<br />\n<br />\nsource：正苦新聞網"},{"pid":"0bf2c10b40ffd3d4ac2b5bbe55ab36e7cca76c87","tid":2076256,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282379c2cc5d103b2a880b3505582adb8452d781","tid":2076256,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:26:04.000Z","msg":"痴線，捐咁少，入到省長個袋都唔夠入市長個袋啦<br />\n我係特首起碼捐夠100億，咁樣可以令村長都有少少錢入袋<br />\n香港市民又唔夠膽嘈<br />\n又可以比中央睇到作為香港市長幫廣大同胞既決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f7b5b03db923b1bf8847826d2585265e0ecdcb","tid":2076256,"uid":360551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bf2c10b40ffd3d4ac2b5bbe55ab36e7cca76c87","tid":2076256,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:26:54.000Z","msg":"咁寒宣，點換車？"},{"pid":"0fdcce8a7187f17ed06148a11e3387d0667c6e75","tid":2076256,"uid":89957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T11:28:02.000Z","msg":"真係得啖笑啦<br />\n又唔用啲錢幫下啲基層市民<br />\n用呢啲錢去啲唔等洗 唔關事嘅地方"},{"pid":"32ce660064b51648046abd097bfd697101908eeb","tid":2076256,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T